        <h1>Defining the Connected Car Experience</h1>

        <p>
          Daimler, the makers of Mercedes-Benz, gave our team six months to help them shape the future of mobility. Our
          goal - develop Mercedesâ€™ first-ever connected car experience. We were to take a human-centered approach
          while leveraging the latest technology to improve the car and driver experience. We designed what the
