        <h3>Deep Sensor & Headunit Integration Across iOS, Android, & Apple Watch</h3>

        <p>
          We interviewed potential end-users to understand them and their relationship with their vehicle. Those
          conversations helped us to validate feature assumptions and identify opportunities for innovation. With a
          tight timeframe, these discoveries also helped us to define what was worth building now.
        </p>

        <!--<%= image_tag("portfolio/fuze_2.jpg", :alt => "Fuze") %>-->

        <p>With the app, drivers could locate their car and remotely lock from anywhere. They could view diagnostics
          such as gas level and tire pressure and get alerted to issues. The app also integrated with the car's head
          unit enhancing in-car navigation capabilities.</p>

        <!--<%= image_tag("portfolio/fuze_5.jpg", :alt => "Fuze") %>-->

        <p>
          This was one of the first ever connected car projects and premiered at Frankfurt Motor Show.
